<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="46" type="topotypical material">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="46">Topotypical material.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="46">Two specimens (LACM-AHF N10947), Panadura River estuary, Sri Lanka, brackish water (donated by T.G. Pillai), October 9, 1961.</paragraph>
